{
  "stem": "1917.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She has only two weeks to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I made a second silent pledge that I will do anything in my power to prove him wrong to survive and be reunited with Merriam.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For the first two weeks, I was between life and death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember most of the time waking up on  the barrack floor as I was crawling, because I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And even in semi-conscious state of mind, I kept telling myself, I must survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I must survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I would fade in and out of consciousness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I-- I looked up in the two sides of the three-story bunk beds filled with this walking dead, or living dead, because they couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "All they could do is scream.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Twice a week, the trucks would come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they would throw them like sacks of potatoes onto the truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the screams were horrifying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was the place where they collected people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a place in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After two weeks, my fever broke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I realized that if I could show them that my fever was going to go down, that somehow they were going to release me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I learned to read the thermometer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two girls who were with me taught me how.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't what disease they had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the nurse came, put in the thermometer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would pull it out, check it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If it was too high, I would shake it down, put it back in, and let it stick out in the back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this way I was in charge of how much fever I was going to have.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was very concerned, because I said, well, I could right now be well and be reunited with Merriam.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was worried that they would become suspicious.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
